- `Settings` -> `Community plugins` -> `Turn on community plugins`
- install: [Excalidraw](obsidian://show-plugin?id=obsidian-excalidraw-plugin)
- enable: Excalidraw
- install: [git](obsidian://show-plugin?id=obsidian-git)
- enable: git
- command: `Obsidian Git: Create backup`
- command: `Obsidian Git: Push`
- install: [admonition](obsidian://show-plugin?id=obsidian-admonition)
- enable: admonition
- install: [sliding panes](obsidian://show-plugin?id=sliding-panes-obsidian)
- enable: sliding panes
- install: [kanban](obsidian://show-plugin?id=obsidian-kanban)
- enable: kanban
- install: [advanced tables](obsidian://show-plugin?id=table-editor-obsidian)
- enable: advanced tables
- install: [auto link title](obsidian://show-plugin?id=obsidian-auto-link-title)
- enable: auto link title
- install: [url into selection](obsidian://show-plugin?id=url-into-selection)
- enable: url into selection
- install: [citation](obsidian://show-plugin?id=obsidian-citation-plugin)
- enable: citation
- install: [ozan's image in editor](obsidian://show-plugin?id=oz-image-plugin)
- enable: ozan's image in editor
- install: [hover editor](obsidian://show-plugin?id=obsidian-hover-editor)
- enable: hover editor
- install: [emoji toolbar](obsidian://show-plugin?id=obsidian-emoji-toolbar)
- enable: emoji toolbar
- `Settings` -> `Appearance` -> `Base theme` -> `Light`
- `Settings` -> `Appearance` -> `Manage`
- install: `Things` theme
